{"tid":2506224,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"嫩白雙球惹火溢出！辜莞允曬愛犬低胸衣下滑　小粉紅險走光","createTime":"2021-04-27T07:18:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T07:28:21.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a6e75929b1aca4a35cbf36eb7f6f3740646530e6","tid":2506224,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:18:01.000Z","msg":"女星辜莞允（Nono）2019年4月被爆偷拍藝人鮪魚（徐瑋吟），雖然最終因證據不足獲不起訴處分，不過她卻因此淡出螢光幕，直到近期才走出陰霾，開始回歸社群平台與粉絲互動。辜莞允昨（26）日特別曬出一張與愛犬巴古膩在一塊的照片，不過眼尖網友卻發現她的低胸上衣下滑，隱私部位險些走光，畫面一出瞬間掀起熱議。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3129242-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3129242-PH.jpg&h=98f4eebf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼擁有甜美臉蛋、火辣身材的辜莞允，近來鮮少在螢光幕前亮相，僅在社群上發辣照與粉絲互動。（圖／翻攝自辜莞允IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3129243-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3129243-PH.jpg&h=597a317f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n辜莞允在IG曬出臉頰緊貼巴古的限時動態，只見她露齒燦笑靠在愛犬身上，巴古則不時撒嬌親她的臉蛋，超萌互動令人看了心花怒放。不過有網友發現，辜莞允超低胸上衣差點包不住好身材，不只超有料上圍、深邃事業線被看光外，隱私處也險些見客，大家紛紛替她捏了一把冷汗，也激動直喊「羨慕巴古」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3129241-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3129241-PH.jpg&h=011688be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼辜莞允PO出與狗狗玩樂的影像，好身材差點走光。（圖／翻攝自辜莞允IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3129245-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3129245-PH.jpg&h=b1cffb3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3129248-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3129248-PH.jpg&h=7a5bb63b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲辜莞允不久也PO出同件套裝展示傲人曲線。（圖／翻攝自辜莞允IG）<br />\n<br />\n辜莞允不久後也PO出穿上同一件套裝出遊的影像，可人臉蛋配上精緻妝容，完美展現女神氣質，往下一看，飽滿雙弧線同樣吸睛，令不少女粉絲羨慕她的好身材與臉蛋。由於裸照門事件影響，辜莞允近期較少作品呈現，因此有許多網友在多則貼文底下詢問「何時會復出呢？」、「好久沒看到辜了喔...」，亦有人祝福她事業能再創巔峰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3129244-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3129244-PH.jpg&h=704124fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼不少粉絲都期待辜莞允能夠走出陰霾早日復出。（圖／翻攝自辜莞允IG）<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3129246-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3129246-PH.jpg&h=282d9d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/04/27/3129247-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F04%2F27%2F3129247-PH.jpg&h=e9a342fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03f67e61114c4337567619c2057e4d11f3b1dd72","tid":2506224,"uid":339805,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:19:14.000Z","msg":"粒lin都睇過晒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ea94983fa59085fd1127c0407bc304a51b06b9","tid":2506224,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:19:41.000Z","msg":"好撚正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815640fba917add02cf164d5d9e1b25cf41200df","tid":2506224,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:19:42.000Z","msg":"米分糹工孚乚豆頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7279ccf75f8816feba50bd44b0439629e1ef39b2","tid":2506224,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03f67e61114c4337567619c2057e4d11f3b1dd72","tid":2506224,"uid":339805,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":4,"replyTime"